4 unit(s) Beyond Meat®
4 unit(s) Artisan Bun
4 unit(s) Corn on the Cob
1 unit(s) Iceberg Lettuce Head
2 unit(s) Tomato
0.13 tsp Salt*
0.13 tsp Pepper*
4 tbsp Oil*

Cut each cob of corn in half crosswise.
Brush each half cob with 1/2 tbsp oil.
Add corn to one side of the grill.
Close lid and grill, turning occasionally, until corn is tender and grill marks form, 8-10 min.
Season with salt and pepper.

Add Beyond Meat patties to the other side of the grill. Close lid and grill, flipping once, until patties are cooked through, 3-4 min per side.**

Thinly slice tomato, then season with salt and pepper.
Remove and discard outer layer of lettuce.
Halve lettuce head, then cut around core.
Separate desired amount of leaves from head. (NOTE: Use remaining lettuce for a future creation!)
Halve buns, then place in the toaster until golden-brown.

Serve alongside your favourite toppings and condiments!